Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.62,0:15:53.32,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,遠比那個叫猿飛佐助要強
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.81,0:15:57.21,mushibugyo_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,久しい　実に久しい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.81,0:15:57.21,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,太久了 真的是太久了
